content:
Inbox mobile is retired as of February 1, 2024. This change applies to Lightning Experience in all editions. Full product retirement was on February 1, 2024.

Replace Inbox mobile with Outlook and Gmail integration with inbox on desktop to access most of the Salesforce Inbox features. On mobile, use the Salesforce mobile application to access Salesforce records, with more exciting functionality coming in a future release. For automatic email tracking, Einstein Activity Capture can also be used.
